{"tid":705400,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【維護前度余香凝】「爺爺」陳家樂：佢冇偷食！","createTime":"2018-06-17T06:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T09:07:15.000Z","uid":161096,"like":4,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"69169311e8b232e960bada9bdfaf98d7d65e1267","tid":705400,"uid":161096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"「爺爺」陳家樂同余香凝分手後，女方負面新聞不停出現，陳家樂今日站出來維護前度，「佢冇偷食！佢唔係咁嘅人，呢件唔係事實，但要一個女仔承受咁大壓力，覺得唔可以囉。」陳家樂話大家冇為呢件事去傾，佢都要時間消化，「我想像唔到件事會被發酵得咁犀利，分手原因我唔想講太多，係我哋兩個人嘅事，況且我哋已經有好好共識。」<br />\n<br />\n陳家樂又話大家在一個月前已分開，唔講嘅原因係大家都各有事業去衝刺，大家在呢段時都有重要嘅工作，想等到完成後，搵最好嘅時機才講，唔係刻意隱瞞大家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JUglSH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JUglSH&d=98R5m9l%2B3%2F2o4DkYFN7880kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ced07099\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JUglSH</a>"},{"pid":"562faa4e7e1919b433d98bb1317b47a9eafc726f","tid":705400,"uid":132587,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"再繼續講就係你消費緊呢段戀情架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fd2a241a970820cc5e5847612c6b7ad92778b1","tid":705400,"uid":82917,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"屌呀，仲講緊喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc8557256d2b7a8541ed030cb7664588189f4a1","tid":705400,"uid":67840,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"多咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95ed93a88f92fcef668df8ed848aec65309d45a","tid":705400,"uid":137700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:55:23.000Z","msg":"就算佢講唔係偷食，我都唔會信囉，臭雞"},{"pid":"57b86edf1da0e71bb47a184e5832aa5dbb7a4815","tid":705400,"uid":55960,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"咁你喊乜鳩"},{"pid":"3c9b7585753c7d9687a2bfbcbc8bfd07790108c2","tid":705400,"uid":16